<hr />
<div class="noprint plainlinks hlist navbar" style="text-align:center;"><span style="word-spacing:0;">This box:</span>
<ul>
<li class="nv-view"><a href="Template_Gospel_Jesus" title="Template:Gospel Jesus"><span title="View this template" style="">view</span></a></li>
<li class="nv-talk"><a href="Template_talk_Gospel_Jesus" title="Template talk:Gospel Jesus"><span title="Discuss this template" style="">talk</span></a></li>
